Abstract: Prohibits employment discrimination based on the misgendering or improper use
of an individual's pronouns.
Proposed law prohibits an employer from terminating or taking any other retaliatory action
against an employee for misgendering or improper use of an individual's pronouns.
(Adds R.S. 23:333)
